{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247383, "create_time": 1655954702, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "这个回答我曾经在zhihu上见到过", "timestamp": 1655954702}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247390, "create_time": 1655954819, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "学生会开始想要独立思考，但又比较叛逆，容易偏激，但又不了解社会的真实，会这样是正常的，只要注意保持冷静不被别有用心煽动就好了。我大伯当年学潮的时候也是非常偏激，但现在谈起来就觉得自己当年有点好笑，现在是真心佩服共产党。", "timestamp": 1655954819}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247398, "create_time": 1655955005, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: dz是反串，你是真的", "timestamp": 1655955005}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247400, "create_time": 1655955141, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Carol: 啊这是反串吗？", "timestamp": 1655955141}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247404, "create_time": 1655955235, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "如果你不是真的认同共产党的一些理念，那之前因为经济进步你去爱戴，之后就会因为经济衰退而去厌恶", "timestamp": 1655955235}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247434, "create_time": 1655955776, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "问题的关键无非在于是否应该把经济腾飞归因于中共的领导及其体制。", "timestamp": 1655955776}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247437, "create_time": 1655955866, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Eve: 当然是有关系的", "timestamp": 1655955866}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247447, "create_tim