55957275, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 你有没有想过，在实际操作上推翻一种体制是需要代价的，任何人都不希望成为代价本身。经济再怎么衰退也是在现在经济的基础上，比共产党刚开始执政的时候好到不知道哪里去了。所以只要经济基本稳定，除非统治者内部发生斗争，政权都会是稳固的。", "timestamp": 1655957275}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247503, "create_time": 1655957327, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Jason: 你只看到了2000年的房价。。", "timestamp": 1655957327}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247508, "create_time": 1655957420, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Jason: 整个社会治安差太大了，回想起来就觉得恐怖…", "timestamp": 1655957420}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247578, "create_time": 1655959150, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 10, "text": "Re Hans: 所以现在的治安真的好吗", "timestamp": 1655959150}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247581, "create_time": 1655959283, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 11, "text": "Re Jason: 比那时自然是好多了，只不过黑社会和人口拐卖的问题一直都没解决", "timestamp": 1655959283}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247587, "create_time": 1655959489, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Jason: 起码走在街上，在家里我不害怕😖", "timestamp": 1655959489}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247589, "create_time": 1655959539, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Jason: 相对的，没说现在的好，只是比以前好太多", "timestamp": 1655959539}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247632, "create_time": 1655960791, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Jason: 所以现在的治安真的不好吗", "timestamp": 1655960791}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 247645, "crea